prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 High Electro Orange features a white leather upper with black overlays and a Hyper Orange ankle wrap. From there, a matching woven tongue label and sole complete the design.

The Air Jordan 1 High Electro Orange released in July of 2021 and retailed for $170.
